latestPosts.caption:
Noor’s 5th birthday 🎈 🧁 03.07.2025

My baby is 5 already and I still don’t believe it 🥹🥹🥹 Watching her become her own little person has truly been my life’s greatest gift 💛🎈

We celebrated her birthday last week at @walk2wonderland and had so much fun.. 

Big thanks to all my friends, my gram squad, Noor’s friends and my family to join in this small celebration 🎉

Big shoutout for the play area @walk2wonderland for organising everything so well. The kids lovedddd the activities that you guys organized - slime making, face painting, bracelet making & balloon moulding.😍💕

The Bunny 🐰 Decor was done by @pinkpurple.event just the way I had imagined. Thanks a lot for bringing my vision of a pink-white subtle bunny theme to life 🩷 

The cake 🎂 was from @whiskcakestudio who is my regular since over 5 years now . Her cakes look the prettiest and are oh! always so delicious 😋 Must Must try their chocolate cherry flavour 🍒

👗Noor’s dress once again is from @theponyandpeonyco (Code: Tanya10)

📸 Video credits: @the_one_who_captures 

Will be sharing all the return gifts 🎁 in a separate reel soon!
